p: \bYou will not just... leave me alone, will you?
\bI've already got the artifact I was looking for.
\bThat up there is a decoy- I was hoping to lure you out to talk.
\bIt's some kind of music... instrument, maybe?
\bI'm not completely sure what it does, but it seems to be a huge source of power.
\bI don't think it's as strong as the crystal but it seems immensely powerful.
\bBut YOU will not stop getting in my way.
\bWhat do you get out of this?
\bYou're not going to stop me. Slow me down, maybe, but I'll just keep coming back.
\bThis is my destiny. I am going to succeed, no matter how many losses I take on the way there.
\bI'm going to knock some sense into you.
\bLearn your lesson now, while you can!
\bTo be fair... I hadn't changed my team at all since we last battled.
\bI wasn't expecting to win. I was only trying to make a point.
\bYou can't hold me down forever, kid.
\bPlus, I have... someone else interested in my efforts.
\bYou're not going to see me losing to you again.
\bI can teach some Pokemon rare and powerful moves that they could only otherwise learn in events.
\bWhat do you want to learn?\ch[2,18,Extreme Speed,Crush Claw,Extrasensory,Flare Blitz,Dragon Ascent,Psycho Boost,Doom Desire,Roar of Time,Spacial
Rend,Secret Sword,Bolt Strike,Blue Flare,V-Create,Relic Song,Shadow Force,Night Shade,Hurricane,(Cancel)]
\bOh, a shame. Maybe another time, then.
